# ExamSpark Teacher Platform Rule

Full spec: [`TEACHER_PLATFORM.md`](TEACHER_PLATFORM.md)

## Teacher Dashboard

Not just upload — **business dashboard** with:
- Student metrics (active, new, expired, renewal due)
- Group analytics (completion, study time, AI questions)
- Student list (plan, joined, expires, last active, credits, progress)
- Business metrics (revenue, subscribers, renewal/churn rate, top lecture/batch)

## Student Access Logic (server-side)

1. Teacher shares lecture → already-joined students: **immediate access**
2. New student joins later → access from **subscription period only**
3. Active subscriber → full access until expiry
4. After expiry → **read-only or locked** (configurable)

## R2 Storage

**Store:** Transcript, Clean Transcript, Notes, Summary, all generated extras, PDF, Images, Teacher Files, Exports

**Never store (default):** Raw Audio — delete after Whisper → save Transcript

Flow: Audio → Whisper → Transcript → delete audio → R2 → Notes → R2

## Groups & Sharing (Strict)

- Teacher owns group; students **cannot** upload, message, or edit
- **Only teacher** shares content (notes, PDF, quiz, etc.)
- Students: **Group Invite Link only** — never content (future: 100 credits configurable)
- Watermark shared assets: `Shared by: {Teacher} • {Group}` + `lecture_id` traceability

Core rules: [`PROJECT_CORE_RULES.md`](PROJECT_CORE_RULES.md)

